dialogue.speaker: Dilbert
dialogue.text: I THOUGHT I HAD THIS TUXEDO THING FIGURED OUT. BUT WHAT THE HECK IS THIS?

dialogue.speaker: Dogbert
dialogue.text: OH, THAT'S THE KUMBERBUZLE. YOU WEAR IT ON YOUR HEAD LIKE A SWEATBAND.

dialogue.speaker: Dogbert
dialogue.text: THEN YOU CLIP YOUR PENS AND PENCILS TO THE KUMBERBUZLE.

dialogue.speaker: Dilbert
dialogue.text: AH, THAT EXPLAINS WHY THE SHIRT HAS NO POCKET.
